=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">解釋把3d print手槍點得黎掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5754fec6e5ce19854562c4c3e3f71313c7687bc8","tid":710830,"uid":65372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:09:24.000Z","msg":"題材本來幾有發揮<br />\n卡士又正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但拍到一舊屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算得90幾分鐘 入面都有好多位係多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e453e2965bb51161795516a89e465bdf574a11","tid":710830,"uid":46587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:17:38.000Z","msg":"成套亂炒炒成唔知乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d97b4f09e49ce2bcc6f5b76750a55a50620f4b","tid":710830,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:01:29.000Z","msg":"黑人細佬同亞洲人好趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成套戲最好睇就係女殺手表演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcb427f6e125bf574b70d383233a83e08aa948e","tid":710830,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:12:30.000Z","msg":"終極垃圾<br />\n劇情幾條支線夾硬駁埋<br />\n打鬥如tvb飛虎<br />\n用科技醫人嗰度仲悶<br />\n邊個想睇點醫人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc98401451a80184506f385776e26f75c43ac98f","tid":710830,"uid":36502,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾到仆街。<br />\n講到酒店個規矩神聖不可侵犯，以為有咩勁人/高科技野守場，點知得個執返黎養大既大隻佬守場，多個保安都冇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出面就繳械入場，入面就係人都拎到手術刀，用得3D printer整槍出黎用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個終極boss咁撚有錢，講到黑白兩道玩哂，都唔搵個好d既醫生醫，係要山長水遠搵個黑市醫生醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個阿婆講到老闆都要守規矩咁型，點知轉頭自己又破壞規矩，d病人殺哂人又覺得冇乜野，仲要幫埋佢地走佬，痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到個黑人咁撚錫個細佬，個細佬比條女害死左，轉頭又咀撚條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到條女咁貪錢，冇啦啦又正義撚上身咁，為左幫個護士走佬而同成班人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個大隻佬保安又唔知做乜撚，留係到送死唔撚走，明明就算贏撚哂都唔會識做醫生，留守間醫院把撚阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到終極boss咁多仔同手下，護士害死左個boss，仲敢返轉頭留守係醫院做乜撚，當係城堡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出面條街攪革命又多9餘，完全對劇情推進係0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n膠撚到咁，都有4.1分！？<br />\n100分滿分阿！？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/011428_6735005e6b94c085a3cea53c6f55c8ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F011428_6735005e6b94c085a3cea53c6f55c8ca.png&h=74be158c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f26c98e4a374c2ceddebb3c796ed08781c29553","tid":710830,"uid":136377,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"33d8d7bbd33410108fb2e2d77b2af8cb3d8e42e7","tid":710830,"uid":107206,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3b35656e0fc207465e3867165e857fe724f58833","tid":710830,"uid":21772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"682b3eafc982fb07e3faefed4b503081e58743aa","tid":710830,"uid":107206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"我都係，有無人可以解答"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T15:45:43.000Z","msg":"好似冇頭冇尾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"完全吾明佢想帶出d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:18:43.000Z","msg":"吾你老母呀！本身睇完套戲